chronic-kidney-disease-due-to-diabetes-m.def:
This causes incorporates death and disability due to chronic kidney disease caused by diabetes type 1.
Chronic kidney disease (CKD) due to diabetes type 1 was responsible for 3·22 million (95% UI 2·28–4·37) DALYs and 7·8% (5·4–10·5) of total overall CKD DALYs.
chronic-kidney-disease-due-to-diabetes-m.name: Chronic kidney disease due to diabetes mellitus type 1

chronic-kidney-disease-due-to-diabetes-m.def:
This causes incorporates death and disability due to chronic kidney disease caused by diabetes type 2.
Chronic kidney disease (CKD) due to diabetes type 2 was responsible for 9·87 million (95% UI 8·11–11·7) DALYs and 23·8% (19·8–27·7) of total overall CKD DALYs.
chronic-kidney-disease-due-to-diabetes-m.name: Chronic kidney disease due to diabetes mellitus type 2

chronic-kidney-disease-due-to-glomerulon.def:
This causes incorporates death and disability due to chronic kidney disease that is due to glomerulonephritis.
Chronic kidney disease (CKD) due to glomerulonephritis was responsible for 6·90 million (95% UI 5·78–8·13) DALYs and 16·6% (14·3–19·2) of total overall CKD DALYs in 2019.
chronic-kidney-disease-due-to-glomerulon.name: Chronic kidney disease due to glomerulonephritis

chronic-kidney-disease-due-to-hypertensi.def:
This causes incorporates death and disability due to chronic kidney disease that is caused by having hypertension.
Chronic kidney disease (CKD) due to hypertension was responsible for 9·96 million (95% UI 8·58–11·5) DALYs and 24·0% (21·0–27·3) of total CKD DALYs.
chronic-kidney-disease-due-to-hypertensi.name: Chronic kidney disease due to hypertension

chronic-kidney-disease-due-to-other-and-.def:
This cause incorporates death and disability due to chronic kidney disease that is due to unknown or unspecified aetiologies.
Chronic kidney disease due to other and unspecified causes was responsible for 11·6 million (95% UI 9·70–13·7) DALYs in 2019.
chronic-kidney-disease-due-to-other-and-.name: Chronic kidney disease due to other and unspecified causes
